Are you crazy?

173
00:05:56,799 --> 00:05:58,098
He's not gonna get parole.

174
00:05:58,133 --> 00:05:59,099
Who's gonna say he deserves it?

175
00:05:59,134 --> 00:06:00,167
You know what, Harvey?

176
00:06:00,202 --> 00:06:01,546
Instead of coming here
and telling me

177
00:06:01,570 --> 00:06:03,381
to betray my cellmate because
Gallo will never get parole,

178
00:06:03,405 --> 00:06:05,083
maybe you should be helping
me get it for him.

179
00:06:05,107 --> 00:06:07,274
I'm never helping that
piece of shit do anything,

180
00:06:07,309 --> 00:06:09,242
and this isn't about Gallo
and you know it.

181
00:06:09,278 --> 00:06:11,556
No, it's about you telling me
to turn on the one guy in here

182
00:06:11,580 --> 00:06:13,780
that I trust based on
some plan that Cahill has

183
00:06:13,816 --> 00:06:15,026
that we don't even
know will work.

184
00:06:15,050 --> 00:06:16,283
No, Mike.

185
00:06:16,318 --> 00:06:18,296
It's about giving you
a chance to get your life back

186
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:20,921
while it still looks the same.

187
00:06:20,956 --> 00:06:23,423
Now, are you going
to take it or not?

