if you're as charming

506
00:17:16,502 --> 00:17:17,613
as you like to think you are.

507
00:17:17,637 --> 00:17:18,714
You know what?
I am charming.

508
00:17:18,738 --> 00:17:19,703
But I'm not an idiot.

509
00:17:19,739 --> 00:17:20,883
And I'm not unwinding my trade

510
00:17:20,907 --> 00:17:23,541
without getting
something in return.

511
00:17:23,576 --> 00:17:26,544
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

512
00:17:26,579 --> 00:17:32,082
