513
00:17:37,023 --> 00:17:38,400
Harvey, I need to talk
to you about something

514
00:17:38,424 --> 00:17:39,390
and you're not going to like it.

515
00:17:39,425 --> 00:17:40,524
About what?

516
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,526
That was Mike
